鼠标是通过hover触发的，是echarts默认配置，没有鼠标事件的额外代码。
下拉框选择后是先dispose，最后setoption，下拉框前几次选择都是没有问题的，tooltip正常关闭。
到达5/6次之后，页面就会出现前一次的tooltip，再选下拉框就会一直叠加。
这个问题我们之前试过3.8.5，和3.8.4 都不能解决，最后3.4.0版本似乎没有这个问题

Basically you don't have to change the code when upgrading to 4.0. The biggest change is that `normal`  status in `itemStyle`, `label`, `areaStyle` will be removed.

So the old code 
```js
itemStyle: {
   normal: {
     color: 'red'
   },
   emphasis: {
     color: 'green'
   }
}
```

Will be written like:
```js
itemStyle: {
  color: 'red'
},
emphasis: {
   itemStyle: { color: 'green' }
}
```

It's much simpler. And the old code can still work.


Others are all new features.  Like new `dataset` component. You can pass the data in common formats without conversion now, which usually can't be avoided in the 3.x version, like following:

```js
option = {
    legend: {},
    tooltip: {},
    dataset: {
        source: [ // data source
            ['product', '2015', '2016', '2017'],
            ['Matcha Latte', 43.3, 85.8, 93.7],
            ['Milk Tea', 83.1, 73.4, 55.1],
            ['Cheese Cocoa', 86.4, 65.2, 82.5],
            ['Walnut Brownie', 72.4, 53.9, 39.1]
        ]
    },
    xAxis: {type: 'category'},
    yAxis: {},
    series: [
        {type: 'bar'},
        {type: 'bar'},
        {type: 'bar'}
    ]
}
```

Or a key-value format data source.

```js
dataset: [{
    source: [
        {product: 'Matcha Latte', count: 823, score: 95.8},
        {product: 'Milk Tea', count: 235, score: 81.4},
        {product: 'Cheese Cocoa', count: 1042, score: 91.2},
        {product: 'Walnut Brownie', count: 988, score: 76.9}
    ]
}, {
    source: {
        'product': ['Matcha Latte', 'Milk Tea', 'Cheese Cocoa', 'Walnut Brownie'],
        'count': [823, 235, 1042, 988],
        'score': [95.8, 81.4, 91.2, 76.9]
    }
}]
```

